      { question: 'Is 3D cell culture experience valuable?', answer: 'Yes. 3D culture systems (spheroids, organoids, organ-on-a-chip) are rapidly replacing traditional 2D cultures for drug screening and disease modeling because they better recapitulate in vivo conditions. Experience with 3D culture is a significant differentiator for research and drug discovery roles.' }
